        "emailType": "text",
        "message": "=Hello {{$node[\"Calculate Lead Score\"].json[\"full_name\"]}},\n\nThank you for contacting us regarding {{$node[\"Calculate Lead Score\"].json[\"service\"]}}.\n\nWe have successfully received your request and our team will review it shortly.\n\nHere\u2019s a quick summary of your inquiry:\n\nCompany: {{$node[\"Calculate Lead Score\"].json[\"company\"]}}\nBudget: ${{$node[\"Calculate Lead Score\"].json[\"budget\"]}}\n\nWe will get back to you within 24 hours.\n\nBest regards,\nLead Capture CRM Team",
